# Privacy Policy for Kesavi Web Solutions

**Last Updated: 15.01.2024**

Welcome to Kesavi Web Solutions! We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines our practices concerning the collection, use, and disclosure of your data.

## 1. Acknowledgment and Acceptance of Terms
- **1.1** By using www.kesaviwebsolutions.com and our services, you consent to the terms of this Privacy Policy.

## 2. Information Collection
- **2.1** We collect information that you provide directly to us, which may include name, email address, phone number, and other personal details.
- **2.2** We also collect indirect information such as browser type, IP address, and cookies, primarily for enhancing your user experience.

## 3. Use of Information
- **3.1** The information we collect is used to provide, maintain, and improve our services, communicate with you, and fulfill any other purpose for which you provide the information.
- **3.2** We may use your information to offer you products or services that may be of interest to you.

## 4. Information Sharing and Disclosure
- **4.1** Kesavi Web Solutions does not sell, trade, or rent your personal identification information to others.
- **4.2** We may share generic aggregated demographic information not linked to any personal identification information with our business partners, trusted affiliates, and advertisers.

## 5. Data Security
- **5.1** We implement appropriate security measures to protect against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction of your personal information.

## 6. Use of Cookies
- **6.1** Our website may use "cookies" to enhance user experience. Users can choose to set their web browser to refuse cookies or to alert you when cookies are being sent.

## 7. Compliance with Childrenâ€™s Online Privacy Protection Act
- **7.1** Protecting the privacy of the very young is especially important. For that reason, we never collect or maintain information on our site from those we know are under 13.

## 8. Changes to This Privacy Policy
- **8.1** Kesavi Web Solutions has the discretion to update this privacy policy at any time. When we do, we will revise the updated date at the top of this page.

## 9. Your Acceptance of These Terms
- **9.1** By using this site, you signify your acceptance of this policy. If you do not agree to this policy, please do not use our site.

## 10. Contacting Us
- **10.1** If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, the practices of this site, or your dealings with this site, please contact us at info@kesaviwebsolutions.com.
